246
00:13:38,242 --> 00:13:41,641
Sebab... Sebab saya rasa dia kelihatan kacak dengannya.

247
00:13:41,642 --> 00:13:45,341
Dia hanya memakai jaket bulu bebiri, jadi...

248
00:13:45,342 --> 00:13:47,241
